g (Auto-Generated)\\n\\nUse the recurring failure patterns below as mandatory hardening checks:\\n- Address this recurring failure mode explicitly: Runtime does not invoke bootstrap_identity on startup, so the identity file is never guaranteed to be created automatically at first run. Severity: blocking.\\n- Address this recurring failure mode explicitly: Add bootstrap_identity() invocation in startup flow (before FirstBootAnnouncer) so first boots mint and persist identity automatically..\\n- Address this recurring failure mode explicitly: Ensure this path is used on both standalone and federated modes..\\n- Enforce behavioral regression tests before completion: Add an integration test that exercises startup and verifies identity persistence between boots..\\n- Enforce behavioral regression tests before completion: Re-run pip install -e '.[dev]' && pytest tests/ -x after wiring the startup path..\\n\"}\n++./sdp/verification/t-001@20260425t183959zb-verify.md:15:{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-25T19:47:24.905Z\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1777146444692_0\",\"status\":\"success\",\"output\":\"90953c8 (HEAD -> feat/graceful-degradation) feat(sampler): on_sampler_free releases scsynth buffer + clears id [T-001@20260425T183959Zb]\\n2efaf10 verify(T-001@20260425T183959Za): verification report — PASS WITH NOTES\\n3c9da82 feat(sampler): on_sampler_load allocates+reads scsynth buffer [T-001@20260425T183959Za]\\n5a5a9b8 verify(T-002@20260425T183959Zd): verification report — PASS\\n3d32c94 feat(sampler): comb damping + decay controls and full-chain integration test [T-002@20260425T183959Zd]\\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/cast_planner.py           |   27 +-\\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/groove_engine.py          |   53 +\\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/music_tracker.py          |  132 +-\\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/sampler_buffers.py        |   75 +\\n progress.md                                        |   49 +-\\n sdp/assumption-log.md                            